data.title: Fanuc (TSE:6954) Valuation After Nvidia Physical AI Robotics Deal and Recent Share Price Surge
data.description: Fanuc (TSE:6954) just jumped nearly 13% after unveiling a collaboration with Nvidia to build industrial robots powered by physical AI, a move that immediately sharpened investor focus on its long term growth story. See our latest analysis for Fanuc. That surge has come on top of already strong momentum, with a 7 day share price return of 18.0% and a 90 day share price return of 44.3%. The 1 year total shareholder return of 52.4% signals investors are steadily warming to Fanuc as physical AI...
